<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="range-n">range <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /reɪndʒ/    美 /reɪndʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>一系列</strong></h4>
<p>a variety of things of a particular type：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a range of</strong> services / products 
一整套服务/一系列产品</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>our new <strong>range of</strong> hair products
我们的新护发产品系列</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>College students come from <strong>a wide range of</strong> social, cultural and economic backgrounds.
大学生们有着不同的社会、文化和经济背景。</p><footer>北师大⑧ – 23改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>范围；界限：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Most of the students are in the 16-19 <strong>age range</strong>. 
大部分学生的年龄在16到19岁之间。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The price was <strong>beyond</strong> our <strong>range</strong>, so we declined.  
那个价格超出了我们能承受的范围，所以我们拒绝了。</p><footer>2015 天津</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>距离：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do not miss this opportunity to see whales <strong>at close range</strong> (= very close) on their annual migration south to the Antarctic.
不要错过近距离观看每年一度南下向南极洲迁徙的鲸群。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 3</footer></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>山脉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Between Italy and France, there is a <strong>mountain range</strong> called the Alps.
在意大利和法国之间，有一座被称作阿尔卑斯山的山脉。</p><footer>外研③ – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-within-range-of">in / within range (of)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在 (…的) 范围内</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="out-of-range-of">out of range (of)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>超出(…的) 范围：</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>This restaurant has become popular for its wide <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (一系列) of foods that suit all tastes and pockets.  （2010 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. range  </p></div>